## 5. CI ワークフロー例（GitHub Actions）

GitHub Actions のワークフロー例も追加しました（必要に応じて調整してください）。

```yaml
 name: Update README Timestamp

 on:
   push:
     paths:
       - scripts/update-readme-timestamp.sh
       - README.md

 jobs:
   update-timestamp:
     runs-on: ubuntu-latest
     steps:
       - uses: actions/checkout@v3
       - name: Update README 最終更新日時
         run: scripts/update-readme-timestamp.sh
       - name: Commit & Push if changed
         run: |
           git config user.name "github-actions[bot]"
           git config user.email "github-actions[bot]@users.noreply.github.com"
           git add README.md
           git diff --cached --exit-code || git commit -m "chore: update README timestamp"
           git push
```
